org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom

Class PlaceObjectNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom.AbstractFXGNode
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom.GraphicContentNode
        • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.fxg.dom.PlaceObjectNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFXGNode, IMaskableNode, IMaskingNode

    public class PlaceObjectNode
extends GraphicContentNode
implements IMaskingNode
    A PlaceObject node does not appear itself in an FXG document but rather represents an instance of a DefinitionNode. An instance may redefine attributes that override the defaults of the definition.
